Name: Thyotis Jackson
Description:
According to police, Thyotis was a cross-dresser working the streets. She was found face down with a cut throat and stab wound.

In April 2010 Ignacio Bulahan, 34, was arrested for her murder.

Name: John D. Mayo
Description: John's body was dismembered by being sawed apart and spread out over a seven mile area. The head has not yet been found.
